<% content_for :title, "About" %>

<div class="row justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-lg-7">
    <h1 class="h3 fw-bold mb-1">About Stay In Touch</h1>
    <p class="text-muted small mb-4">Northwestern CS Software Studio, Spring 2026</p>

    <div class="vstack gap-4">
      <section>
        <p class="text-muted">Stay In Touch is a personal CRM for keeping up with friends. Track the people you care about. Log your catch-ups. See at a glance who you owe a call. No formal reminder needed.</p>
        <p class="text-muted">We built it as a class project for Northwestern's CS Software Studio.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">How to Use</h2>
        <dl class="row text-muted mb-0">
          <dt class="col-sm-3"><i class="bi bi-person me-1"></i>People</dt>
          <dd class="col-sm-9">Contacts you want to stay in touch with. For each person you set a catch-up frequency (e.g. every 2 weeks) and preferred hours — Stay In Touch uses this to remind you when you're overdue.</dd>
          <dt class="col-sm-3"><i class="bi bi-calendar-check me-1"></i>Events</dt>
          <dd class="col-sm-9">The actual catch-ups you log — a coffee, a call, a text. Each event is linked to one or more people and resets the countdown for when you're next due to reach out.</dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Team</h2>
        <ul class="text-muted">
          <li>Matthew Khoriaty</li>
          <li>Rohit Katakam</li>
          <li>Joshua Yao</li>
          <li>Tais Martinez</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Source code</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          <%= link_to "github.com/NU-CS-Software-Studio-Spring-26/project-stay-in-touch",
                "https://github.com/NU-CS-Software-Studio-Spring-26/project-stay-in-touch",
                target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" %>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-4"><%= link_to "← Back", :back, class: "text-muted small" %></p>
  </div>
</div>
